creating the game 2048 using javascript 

first action will be to create the game board making a 4x4 board

when starting the game the first blocks will drop and not overlap each other if the block is taken

making sure the blocks only combine when they have same value and player moves blocks in direction where blocks collide

once block combines they double in value

they do not combine if blocks that colide into each other have different values

if block has no space in the direction the player moves it will not move unless able to combin

each move player makes will drop more blocks with value of 2

player can restart game when wanted and game keeps score of highest number the player was able to get
